query:
INSERT INTO courses (
  regionId,
  title,
  description,
  framework,
  level,
  durationHours,
  price,
  price3Month,
  price6Month,
  price12Month,
  modules,
  prerequisites,
  certificationRequired,
  active,
  createdAt,
  updatedAt
) VALUES (
  1,
  'EU AI Act Fundamentals',
  'Comprehensive 8-module course covering the EU AI Act regulation. Learn prohibited practices, high-risk AI systems, provider/deployer obligations, transparency requirements, GPAI regulation, governance structure, compliance timeline, and penalties. Includes real-world examples, case studies, and practical compliance roadmaps. Certification upon completion.',
  'EU AI Act',
  'fundamentals',
  10,
  49900,
  19900,
  9900,
  5900,
  '[{"title":"Introduction to the EU AI Act","description":"Learn the purpose, scope, and regulatory framework","durationMinutes":45,"content":"# Module 1: Introduction to the EU AI Act\\n\\nComprehensive introduction covering the purpose, scope, and key concepts of the EU AI Act..."},{"title":"Risk Classification System","description":"Understand the four risk categories and how to classify AI systems","durationMinutes":45,"content":"# Module 2: Risk Classification System\\n\\nLearn how to classify AI systems by risk level..."},{"title":"Prohibited AI Practices","description":"Identify all 8 prohibited practices and enforcement timeline","durationMinutes":60,"content":"# Module 3: Prohibited AI Practices\\n\\nDetailed coverage of all prohibited AI practices..."},{"title":"High-Risk AI Systems - Part 1","description":"Annex III Categories 1-4: Biometric, Infrastructure, Education, Employment","durationMinutes":60,"content":"# Module 4: High-Risk AI Systems - Part 1\\n\\nComprehensive coverage of first 4 Annex III categories..."},{"title":"High-Risk AI Systems - Part 2","description":"Annex III Categories 5-8: Essential Services, Law Enforcement, Migration, Justice","durationMinutes":60,"content":"# Module 5: High-Risk AI Systems - Part 2\\n\\nCoverage of remaining 4 Annex III categories..."},{"title":"Provider and Deployer Obligations","description":"All 12 provider obligations and 7 deployer obligations","durationMinutes":60,"content":"# Module 6: Provider and Deployer Obligations\\n\\nComplete guide to compliance obligations..."},{"title":"Transparency, GPAI, and Governance","description":"Transparency requirements, GPAI regulation, and governance structure","durationMinutes":60,"content":"# Module 7: Transparency, GPAI, and Governance\\n\\nLearn transparency obligations and GPAI requirements..."},{"title":"Compliance Timeline, Penalties, Next Steps","description":"Phased implementation timeline, penalty structure, and compliance roadmap","durationMinutes":60,"content":"# Module 8: Compliance Timeline, Penalties, Next Steps\\n\\nNavigate the compliance timeline and develop your roadmap..."}]',
  '[]',
  TRUE,
  TRUE,
  NOW(),
  NOW()
)
